hwt.bodyText:
If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        wr_ptr(0x0),
        size_reg(0x0),
        rd_ptr(0x0),
        looped(0x0),
    ).Else(
        wr_ptr(wr_ptr_next),
        size_reg(size_reg_next),
        rd_ptr(rd_ptr_next),
        looped(looped_next),
    ),
)

If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        uploadedCntr(0x0),
        timeoutCntr(1024 - 1.auto_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
        st(st_t.waitOnInput),
        remaining(512.auto_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
        offset(0x0),
        lastWordCntr(0x0),
    ).Else(
        uploadedCntr(uploadedCntr_next),
        timeoutCntr(timeoutCntr_next),
        st(st_next),
        remaining(remaining_next),
        offset(offset_next),
        lastWordCntr(lastWordCntr_next),
    ),
)

If((st._eq(st_t.waitOnInput)) & ((sig_buff_size._eq(16.auto_cast(Bits(5, signed=False, forceVector=True)))) | (timeoutCntr._eq(0x0))),
    wDatapump_req_vld(0x1),
    If(wDatapump_req_rd,
        If((remaining - 1) < buffSize_tmp,
            offset_next(0x0),
            remaining_next(512.auto_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
        ).Else(
            offset_next(offset + (Concat(Bits(5, forceVector=True).fromPy(0x0), (sig_buff_size)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5, forceVector=True))))._reinterpret_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
            remaining_next(remaining - (Concat(Bits(5, forceVector=True).fromPy(0x0), (sig_buff_size)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5, forceVector=True))))._reinterpret_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
        ),
        sizeOfItems_next((sizeTmp)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5, forceVector=True))),
        timeoutCntr_next(1024 - 1.auto_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
    ).Else(
        offset_next(offset),
        remaining_next(remaining),
        sizeOfItems_next(sizeOfItems),
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr),
    ),
).Else(
    wDatapump_req_vld(0x0),
    If((sig_buff_dataOut_vld._eq(0x1)) & (st._eq(st_t.waitOnInput)) & (timeoutCntr != 0x0),
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr - 1),
    ).Else(
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr),
    ),
    offset_next(offset),
    remaining_next(remaining),
    sizeOfItems_next(sizeOfItems),
)

If((remaining - 1) < buffSize_tmp,
    wDatapump_req_len((sig_)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4, forceVector=True))),
    sizeTmp(sig_),
).Else(
    wDatapump_req_len((sig_)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4, forceVector=True))),
    sizeTmp(sig_buff_size),
)
